1Kp2anZbCt","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recat3XylBUUNw22a","target":"recmXmhZt51doQu7o","label":"event"},{"source":"recat3XylBUUNw22a","target":"rechX4p94qqiHLqLx","label":"event"},{"source":"recat3XylBUUNw22a","target":"recUlD55WynUKdHAo","label":"event"},{"source":"recat3XylBUUNw22a","target":"rec7pLeyxV0yEdrcl","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recSPsdO2gsT86iHH","ref":"John.19.1","text":"Then Pilate therefore took Jesus, and scourged him.","year":33},{"id":"recUAaCF1iIVFWuVH","ref":"John.19.2","text":"And the soldiers platted a crown of thorns, and put it on his head, and they put on him a purple robe,","year":33},{"id":"rec5JSmZen46ZOYIu","ref":"John.19.3","text":"And said, Hail, King of the Jews! and they smote him with their hands.","year":33},{"id":"recisErR8ogDe7oGe","ref":"John.19.4","text":"Pilate therefore went forth again, and saith unto them, Behold, I bring him forth to you, that ye may know that I find no fault in him.","year":33},{"id":"recxnfJLmUDvf7xEm","ref":"John.19.5","text":"Then came Jesus forth, wearing the crown of thorns, and the purple robe. And Pilate saith unto them, Behold the man!","year":33},{"id":"recq571ihjAr22P32","ref":"John.19.6","text":"When the chief priests therefore and officers saw him, they cried out, saying, Crucify him, crucify him. Pilate saith unto them, Take ye him, and crucify him: for I find no fault in him.","year":33},{"id":"recyfdAHJjTzsoJFQ","ref":"John.19.7","text":"The Jews answered him, We have a law, and by our law he ought to die, because he made himself the Son of God.","year":33},{"id":"recE3sHFu0Qb14QXk","ref":"John.19.8","text":"When Pilate therefore heard that saying, he was the more afraid;","year":33}]}
